{"tid":1600704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非真係舒服,可以行街睇戲食飯溝女去船P,今次我真係和理非大進步","createTime":"2019-09-28T17:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T00:15:27.000Z","uid":241151,"like":3,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"edc3b8a15134c3eddf69f8bde225ee7da08afe37","tid":1600704,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:05:11.000Z","msg":"和理非既進步點會去咗變勇武?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非既定位係和平理性非暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,如果變勇武既方向,點都係退步啦,完全係反和理非既原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以勇武就勇武,和理非就和理非,定位完全唔同<br />\n和理非既升level緊係越來越連粗口都唔講得, 咁先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 變勇武?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪墮落囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知班泛民左膠又唔岩聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3fcc0c0756b6d0d0110f7d9b9e005512454807","tid":1600704,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:07:50.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"90e9d0a06d6de509d6f825d47364d2c0b3dc40bc","tid":1600704,"uid":200758,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:08:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請善用不推文回覆</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"70251001e555bfe12b2f11a36a2a3bc7c5a9bd2d","tid":1600704,"uid":241151,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"90e9d0a06d6de509d6f825d47364d2c0b3dc40bc","tid":1600704,"uid":200758,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:08:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx